data.description: UPGRADES, UPGRADES, UPGRADES!  Welcome home to this 4 bedroom, 3 bath stunner on an oversized lot with water front and nature views. Split floor plan with large master suite, expansive living area and 9 foot ceilings throughout. Gourmet kitchen with 48'' wooden cabinets, quartz counters, custom backsplash, vent hood, accent lighting and plenty of pantry storage. Spacious dining room with accent wall for family gatherings.  Relax on the screened lanai or gather on the paver patio to enjoy water views and nature. There is also a deluxe aluminum  fence for Fido and a 50 amp breaker for a hot tub. Three car garage for all of your toys with built in storage and a new epoxy floor. New bathroom fixtures, barndoors and upgraded ceiling fans are a bonus. Make your appointment today!
